        <div class="msgSubject">Feint, waiting to get nerfed.</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-03 08:27:28   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1288794448301076677" id="quote-1288794448301076677" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1288794448301076677" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=186&amp;mid=1288794448301076677&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1288794448301076677&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1288794448301076677" onclick="followToggle('add','1288794448301076677')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
