      <div class="msgContentFrame">Well more damage do means more SP per proc (Not the chance to get SP), that's why I do prefer heavy hitting skill because if it do give SP, it gives a large chunk (200+) helping me cap my SP gain relatively quick. And IMO any kill that take longer than 40 seconds will mean a general drop in SP/HR. The Black Eft spots near Nine Ives have notoriously high spawn rate and it's not uncommon to have 2 Eft 3 Buzzard jump on you if you take too long to kill one Eft. Fast spawn also equals to fast SP gain per hour, if you do fast kill.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1807831.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></div></div>
